Sentencas: Two Fe-based alloys, specific company developed and designated as Crofer22APU and ZMG232, have been extensively evaluated and considered as outstanding metallic interconnect materials.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnect coated with La-Sr-Mn film by screen painting and plasma sputtering

Sentencas: Both these alloys contain significant and minute amounts of elemental Cr and La, respectively.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnect coated with La-Sr-Mn film by screen painting and plasma sputtering

Sentencas: In this study, they are coated with films of La-Sr-Mn (LSM) using two methods, screen painting and plasma sputtering, to determine the effect of LSM on corrosion resistance and electrical resistivity of Crofer22APU and ZMG232.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnect coated with La-Sr-Mn film by screen painting and plasma sputtering

Sentencas: They were then treated in a simulated oxidizing environment at 800 degrees C for 200 h. Analytical results indicate that the LSM film changed the oxidation behavior of the base alloys, Crofer22APU and ZMG232.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnect coated with La-Sr-Mn film by screen painting and plasma sputtering

Sentencas: The bare alloys formed Cr2O3, while the coated alloys produced (Mn, Fe) Cr2O4.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnect coated with La-Sr-Mn film by screen painting and plasma sputtering

Sentencas: The electrical resistance of the former oxide at high temperature is several thousand times higher than that of the latter oxide.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnect coated with La-Sr-Mn film by screen painting and plasma sputtering

Sentencas: This remarkable effect of the LSM film on the electrical characteristics warrants further in-depth research.
Titulo: Oxidation behavior of metallic interconnect coated with La-Sr-Mn film by screen painting and plasma sputtering
